### Get all products
GET http://localhost:9000/api/products

### Get product by ID
GET http://localhost:9000/api/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE

### Get cart (requires token)
GET http://localhost:9000/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Get cart total
GET http://localhost:9000/api/cart/total
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Add to cart
POST http://localhost:9000/api/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{"productId": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE"}

### Remove from cart
DELETE http://localhost:9000/api/cart/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Change cart quantity
PUT http://localhost:9000/api/cart/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{"quantity": 3}

### Get wishlist
GET http://localhost:9000/api/wishlist
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Add to wishlist
POST http://localhost:9000/api/wishlist
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{"productId": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE"}

### Remove from wishlist
DELETE http://localhost:9000/api/wishlist/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Create order (checkout)
POST http://localhost:9000/api/checkout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
